\int_0^1f_n(x)dx=\int_0^1nx(1-x)^ndx=\frac n{n+1}\int_0^1(1-x)^{n+1}dx=-\frac{n}{(n+1)(n+2)}(1-x)^{n+2}\Big|_0^1=\frac{n}{(n+1)(n+2)}\to0=\int_0^1\lim_{n\to\infty}f_n(x)dx
